{"tid":1069873,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟結完婚生仔係為左乜","createTime":"2019-03-20T09:01:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T05:42:07.000Z","uid":62551,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"364cd36accb8422523f1e6097c6bbd1fbb950861","tid":1069873,"uid":62551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T09:01:21.000Z","msg":"生仔同有錢係咪掛勾左<br />\n生仔係有錢既表現<br />\n<br />\n窮人唔好生仔 我明<br />\n有錢人生仔 係同金錢掛勾？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有錢係咪就代表做到一個稱職既父母<br />\n<br />\n教育係唔係同金錢掛勾左<br />\n有錢人可以比最好既物質比個仔 咁品格品德係咪可以用錢就教育到<br />\n<br />\n眼見而家大多都係有錢但唔識教育"},{"pid":"e5a3fcddc4aa05b92a18fc8240f775c82fad77a1","tid":1069873,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T09:37:26.000Z","msg":"妳係咪有問題呀？精神有冇病呀？打八百幾次電話畀人？咁無聊嘅妳，妳再做呢啲嘢，我一定捉妳去睇吓係咪傻嘅！"},{"pid":"963ac41f80b04abd26acf5ed8470ccbeb2ed170d","tid":1069873,"uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T09:44:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images7.memedroid.com/images/UPLOADED679/577d1a35cfaaf.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages7.memedroid.com%2Fimages%2FUPLOADED679%2F577d1a35cfaaf.jpeg&h=4721ed24&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e799c0857c1cdbe21b9094b2e9adc8742af42e3a","tid":1069873,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T05:42:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}